dcterms:description: The Weimar Jazz Database (WJazzD) comprises 456 monophonic Jazz solos, each arranged in lead sheet style with melody and beat tracks, containing detailed annotations for pitch, onset time, duration, loudness, chord progressions, and structural markings, all human-annotated and cross-checked for data cleanliness.
dcterms:title: Weimar Jazz Database (WJazzD)
